Package gamelogic.player

Class PlayerFactoryMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • gamelogic.player.PlayerFactoryMethod
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlayerFactory
    public class PlayerFactoryMethod
extends java.lang.Object
implements PlayerFactory
    The class for the PlayerFactoryMethod! PlayerFactoryMethod will be used to create new types of players in the pentago game. The types of players include computer player, human player and the network player. Implements the interface PlayerFactory.
